INSERT INTO `products` VALUES (1,'DEWALT-DCF887B 20 V MAX* XR Brushless',' 20 V MAX* XR Brushless 1/4-in 3-Speed Impact Driver (Bare)',100,25,2,'2021-06-07 20:21:43','2021-06-07 20:21:43'),(2,'DEWALT-DCPW550B 20V Max 550 PSI Power Cleaner ',' <strong>20V Max 550 PSI Power Cleaner (Tool Only)</strong>\nPortable cleaning on the jobsite or at home with 10X the cleaning power with the DEWALT 20V Max Power Cleaner.<br/>\n This tool can draw from any fresh water source with an included suction hose where a garden hose is not easily accessible. It can also be hooked up to your garden hose at home or on the jobsite with the convenient quick connect adaptor. This tool is ideal for convenient cleaning of tools and equipment as well as decks, boats, outdoor furniture and vehicles. It comes with 4 nozzles that all stored on the unit as well as a soap bottle to cover all your cleaning tasks. Part of the 20V Max DEWALT system this tool will be a great addition to your collection.',149,15,2,'2021-06-07 20:27:32','2021-06-10 13:48:41'),(3,'DEWALT-DCW210B 20 V MAX* Brushless 5-in Random Orbit Sander  ',' 20 V MAX* Brushless 5-in Random Orbit Sander (Bare Tool)\n\nOur 20V MAX XR brushless 5-in cordless random orbital sander provides users with the power and runtime needed to complete their jobs. A variable-speed dial provides ultimate speed control from 8,000 – 12,000 OPM for a variety of projects. One-handed locking dust bag attaches securely to the sander to aid in dust collection or the user can attach the sander directly to the DWV010 or DWV012 dust collectors. Rubber overmolded grip provides comfortable sanding. Replacement 8-hole hook-and-loop sanding pad for quick, easy paper changing.',99,20,2,'2021-06-07 20:29:39','2021-06-07 20:29:39'),(4,'DEWALT-DCF889HB',' 20 V MAX XR Brushless High Torque 1/2-in Impact Wrench w. Hog Ring Anvil Bare\nThe DCF899HB 20 V MAX XR brushless high torque 1/2-in impact wrench w. Hog ring anvil is powerful and versatile for fastening various applications. Designed for comfort, speed control, and working in dark spaces.',249,10,2,'2021-06-07 20:32:47','2021-06-07 20:32:47'),(5,'DEWALT-DCS380B 20 V Max Li-ion Reciprocating Saw ',' 20 V Max Li-ion Reciprocating Saw (Tool Only)\nFloors, corners and other hard-to-reach areas are no match for this 20-volt reciprocating saw. The variable-speed motor delivers 0-3,000-SPM for faster cutting and increased control, while the trigger lock provides enhanced safety when the saw is not in use. The compact design and 4-position blade clamp allow versatility when limited clearance is available, making it possible to tackle flush-cutting from nearly any angle. When you need a fresh blade or are switching between tasks, the tool-free clamp means you waste less time changing out the blade and can spend more time finishing the job. The comfortable, over-molded rubber grip reduces fatigue and improves control, even on heavy-duty tasks or when working for longer durations. Floors, corners and other hard-to-reach areas are no match for this 20-volt reciprocating saw. The variable-speed motor delivers 0-3,000-SPM for faster cutting and increased control, while the trigger lock provides enhanced safety when the saw is not in use. The compact design and 4-position blade clamp allow versatility when limited clearance is available, making it possible to tackle flush-cutting from nearly any angle. When you need a fresh blade or are switching between tasks, the tool-free clamp means you waste less time changing out the blade and can spend more time finishing the job. The comfortable, over-molded rubber grip reduces fatigue and improves control, even on heavy-duty tasks or when working for longer durations.\n',99,20,2,'2021-06-07 20:34:55','2021-06-07 20:34:55'),(6,'BOSCH-11255VSR SDS-Plus® Bulldog™ Extreme Rotary Hammer',' 1 In. SDS-Plus® Bulldog™ Extreme Rotary Hammer  The 1-Inch SDS-Plus® Bulldog™ Xtreme Rotary Hammer from BOSCH makes it easy to drill holes into tough material. It has a 7.5-Amp motor that generates up to 2 foot-pounds of impact energy per blow to make quick work of hard projects. This Bosch 1-inch SDS-plus Bulldog rotary hammer\'s Vario-Lock™ design lets you set the chisel position to one of 36 different settings for working at different angles. You can run this versatile tool in rotation, hammer or rotary hammer modes. The Bosch rotary hammer\'s SDS-plus chisel retention system transfers power efficiently and allows for easy bit changes. It has a variable-speed reverse design, which gives you the same power going in forward or reverse gear. The D-handle gives you greater comfort and more leverage for easy control. This tools integral clutch keeps it from binding up for more consistent work. When not in use, the HammerHook™ allows for convenient storage.',179,15,7,'2021-06-08 07:57:32','2021-06-08 07:57:32'),(7,'BOSCH-GBH2-28-L SDS-plus® Bulldog™ Xtreme Max 1-1/8 In. Rotary Hammer',' SDS-plus® Bulldog™ Xtreme Max 1-1/8 In. Rotary Hammer\n\nThe Bosch GBH2-28L SDS-plus® Bulldog™ Xtreme Max 1-1/8 In. Rotary Hammer features a powerful 8.5 Amp motor and KickBack Control. This feature is an integrated sensor to stop tool rotation during bit bind-up situations. A tool that upholds the tradition in the line of legendary Bosch Bulldog hammers, the GBH2-28L combines user comfort with versatile drilling and hammering functions. It provides counter-balanced Vibration Control for more comfortable handling of the hammer. Ideal for masonry pros or general contractors, this tool weighs only 6.9 Lbs. but delivers 2.4 Ft.-Lbs. of impact energy and 0-5,100 BPM. It has a multifunction mode selector for drilling versatility – drilling only, hammer drilling and chiseling. This Bulldog has ideal features for hard-working pros, including a variable-speed reversing trigger for accurate bit starting, Vario-Lock positioning for the optimal chiseling angle, a HammerHook that allows the user to hang the tool on the job and an ergonomic D-handle for user comfort. The SDS-plus® system provides for tool-free bit changes.',239,25,7,'2021-06-08 08:01:14','2021-06-08 08:01:14'),(8,'BOSCH-GWX10-45DE 4-1/2 In.X-LOCK Ergonomic Angle Grinder',' 4-1/2 In. X-LOCK Ergonomic Angle Grinder with No Lock-On Paddle Switch\nThe Bosch GWX10-45DE 4-1/2 In. X-LOCK angle grinder features the X-LOCK mount, offering a wheel change interface that\'s up to five times faster than conventional interfaces. There’s an audible snap when mounting an X-LOCK Wheel on an X-LOCK grinder. The wheel mounts properly without the need for a spanner wrench or flange nuts. The wheel is released from the grinder with the pull of a lever. The GWX10-45DE ergonomic grinder features a narrow grip zone for extended comfort and control, combined with a powerful 10-amp motor. It delivers results, producing up to 11,000 no-load rpm for maximum productivity in grinding and cutting applications. The tool weighs 4.6 Lbs. The no-lock-on paddle switch function provides rapid shutdown of the motor after the switch is released. Equipped with epoxy-coated field windings, double seals on the gear housing and direct-motor cooling, this grinder is built for a longer tool life. It features spiral bevel gears for smooth transmission of power. For added convenience, it has an auxiliary handle and an adjustable tool-free guard.',99,17,7,'2021-06-08 08:07:56','2021-06-08 08:07:56'),(9,'BOSCH-GWS13-50VS 5 In. Angle Grinder',' 5 In. Angle Grinder\n\nThe Bosch GWS13-50VS 5- In. Angle Grinder delivers more power than previous-generation models with the same size tool – 13 amps and up to 11,500 RPM. The lower variable-speed setting – 2,800 RPM – allows the operator to match speed to application. For operator comfort and control, it sports a two-position Vibration Control side handle, making it less demanding to run. The grinder has constant electronics for easy starts, level operation and dependable speed under load. For user security, it an integrated acceleration sensor to limit inadvertent recoil and restart protection to protect against unintended startup. It has a burst-protection quick toolless adjustable guard and a large spindle lock for more convenient disc change. It was designed with directed air flow to divert dust from vital components, direct-motor cooling and Service Minderbrushes that stop the grinder when preventative maintenance is required – which promote longer tool life.',129,8,7,'2021-06-08 08:10:26','2021-06-08 08:10:26'),(10,'BOSCH-GWS9-45 4-1/2 In Angle Grinder',' 4-1/2 In Angle Grinder\n\nThe Bosch GWS9-45 4-1/2-in. Angle grinder is a light, handy grinder with plenty of power – 8.5 amps and 11,000 RPM. It has direct-motor cooling, giving it higher overload capabilities, and it has directed air flow that diverts dust away from vital components. This grinder has a two-position side handle. It has a burst-protection quick tool less adjustable guard, a fast-change disc change and a large spindle lock. Thermoluminescence brushes stop the grinder when preventative maintenance is required.',69,25,7,'2021-06-08 08:12:36','2021-06-08 08:12:36'),(11,'Makita XGT 40V max Rotary Hammer 1 9/16\" AVT, Bare Tool',' Makita XGT 40V max Rotary Hammer 1 9/16\" AVT, Bare Tool\nThe 40V max XGT® Brushless 1-9/16” AVT® Rotary Hammer (GRH05Z, tool only) is a cordless concrete solution designed for heavy-load applications. It delivers the power, speed, and run-time for corded demands, without the cord. The GRH05Z features Active Feedback-Sensing Technology (AFT®), which electronically turns off the motor if rotation of bit is suddenly forced to stop, and Anti-Vibration Technology (AVT®) for reduced vibration. More than just a padded handle, AVT is an internal counterbalance that uses air pressure to move counterweight pistons in the opposite direction of the drive piston to actively reduce vibration. In addition, the vibration-absorbing back handle and side handle further reduce vibration. For added durability in harsh job site conditions, Extreme Protection Technology (XPT™) is engineered for improved dust and water resistance. Auto-Start Wireless System (AWS®) uses Bluetooth® technology for wireless power-on and power-off communication between the equipped tool and dust extractor. Once connected via AWS, the AWS-equipped dust extractor will automatically power on or off when the AWS-equipped cordless tool starts or stops, running only when the tool is in use. This increases productivity on a single charge and reduces continuous noise at the job or work site.',669,5,1,'2021-06-08 08:34:37','2021-06-08 08:34:37'),(12,'Makita XGT 40V max Circular Saw, Rear Handle 7 1/4”, Bare Tool',' Makita XGT 40V max Circular Saw, Rear Handle 7 1/4”, Bare Tool\n\nThe 40V max XGT® Brushless Rear Handle 7-1/4” Circular Saw (GSR01Z) provides cordless convenience, while taking on high-demand applications. The Makita-built brushless motor delivers 6,400 RPM for high-speed cutting performance. It cuts 3X the material in a single pass with a large cutting capacity of 2-9/16”. This saw is ideal for framers, builders, roofers, forming, and more. The GSR01Z offers 56-degrees bevel capacity with positive stops at 22.5-degrees and 45-degrees and a bevel up to 56-degrees. The saw features an electric brake for maximum productivity and a die-cast magnesium base. Automatic Torque Drive Technology adjusts cutting speed under load for optimum cutting performance. The saw is also equipped with Makita\'s Extreme Protection Technology (XPT™), is a series of integrated seals designed to improve a tool’s operation in harsh conditions by channeling water and dust from key internal components. XGT is a system of equipment, tools, batteries, and chargers utilizing 40v max lithium-ion batteries. XGT is engineered to deliver high power to take on high-demand applications, allowing users to completely transition to a cordless job site. XGT is equipped with advanced brushless motor engineering, intelligent digital communication, and superior durability featur